# Day-1 Go-Live Readiness Framework

Hospital IT go-live success depends on preparedness, not perfection.

## Critical Success Factors
- All clinical workflows must function without disruption
- IT support must be visible and accessible
- Escalation paths must be clear
- Downtime procedures must be known

## Day-1 Focus Areas
- OPD registration and billing
- IPD admission and discharge
- Laboratory sample processing
- Radiology reporting
- Pharmacy operations

## On-Go-Live Best Practices
- War-room setup with stakeholders
- Real-time issue tracking
- Immediate decision-making authority
- Clear communication to clinical teams
